Bangladesh Police and the Rapid Action Battalion (RAB) abducted from his home in 
Rajshahi Mr Anwarul Islam Masum, a university student and the Rajshahi City Office 
Secretary of Bangladesh Islami Chhatra Shibir (BICS), which is the student wing of 
Jamaat-e-Islami, an opposition political party. Mr Anwarul Islam Masum was 
reportedly taken inside a RAB vehicle and driven away to an unknown place. He may 
be at risk of torture or extra-judicial execution. 
