revealed Mr Nguyen Van Hai&#8217;s on-going hunger strike. Mr Nguyen Van Hai had been 
subjected to torture in the past and held two hunger strikes to protest against his 
detention, the most recent of which started on 23 June 2013. Similarly, Mr Cu Huy Ha 
Vu was on hunger strike from 27 May to 21 June 2013to protest against his detention. 
