Le Son, Nguyen Van Duyet, Nguyen Van Oai, Ho Van Oanh, Nguyen Dinh Cuong, 
Nguyen Xuan Anh, Thai Van Dung, Tran Minh Nhat, Nong Hung Anh, Nguyen Dang 
Vinh Phuc, Nguyen Dang Minh Man and Dang Ngoc Minh were convicted and sentenced 
to prison terms ranging from 3 to 13 years by the People&#8217;s Court of Nghe An on charges 
